episodes.text: Would you like to be able in a short time to create a whiteboard presentation like this?
Or may be you are a professor.
And would like to explain a formula to a student
In case you were wondering about this voice... I can use some other voices too
In some more business use cases, one may want to show a table of products revenue
Or maybe a sales person would like to explain exactly how a product works.
So how does it all work? In the core of everything is a script. A script contains steps.
Some steps draw shapes, others draw text.
And yet others play speech recordings.
